titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 4-fluoro-3-phenoxy benzaldehyde.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S5945)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/13/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1995, the duty on 4-Fluoro-3-phenoxy benzaldehyde.
